Veteran Tanzanian singer Rehema Chalamila, popularly known as Ray C, is expecting her first child with her mzungu bae. She announced the news on Monday by sharing a cute video capturing her protruding belly. Ray C used Singer Joel Lwanga and Barnaba Classic's song 'Sayuni' as the accompaniment for her video. “Wakati wa Mungu ni wakati sahihi,” she captioned the video. In 2019, Ray C talked about losing a pregnancy. She asked women to advise her on how to keep a pregnancy to avoid having a miscarriage. She went on to say that she was in pain after losing her child and she couldn’t keep quiet about it. Ray C also shared a picture of herself in hospital. A few months before then, she confessed that she had contemplated suicide due to depression.